title: Sam Kitchen
summary: Sam Kitchen (born 6 April 1994) is an Australian rugby union player for Edinburgh in the Pro14. Kitchen's primary position is hooker.
content:
Sam Kitchen (born 6 April 1994) is an Australian rugby union player for Edinburgh in the Pro14. Kitchen's primary position is hooker.


== Rugby Union career ==


=== Professional career ===
Kitchen represented Sydney Rays before moving to Scotland to join Ayrshire Bulls. He joined Edinburgh in June 2020.
